{{Noticebox/Official}}{{Noticebox/Stub}}[[File:VRChat VirtualEvents.webp|thumb|VRChat has multiple events, hosted from around the world that can be attended by anyone!]]
Official events and Jams are a way for [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]] to engage with the community, by allowing creators to showcase their creativity in Jams, or socializing and connecting with others with Events.

Multiple events are handled every day on the platform, notable events are organized by VRChat themselves or in collaboration with partners to create memorable experiences. Check out some notable [[Special:MyLanguage/:Category:Events|community events]]!

==Events==

===New Year's Eve ===
[[File:NYE KeyArt v2 FirstPass.png|thumb|200x200px|New Year's Eve 2024 key art]]
VRChat New Year's Eve is an annual event to celebrate and ring in the new year!

Hosted in a mock version of New York City Times Square, where users can hang out and socialize with people from around the world, watching the ball drop for every time zone around the world. The world includes community booths and posters from users to showcase themselves and their creations. And either musical performances or video entertainment to keep the party going!

''Check out the [[Special:MyLanguage/New Years Eve|New Year's Eve]] page for more information.''

===Spookality===
[[File:Spookality KeyArt 2023 SocialMedia NowLive.png|thumb|250x250px|Spookality 2023 key art]]
Spookality is an annual Halloween-themed avatar and world jam where users showcase their spooky and bizarre avatars and worlds.

Users can view all the highlighted submissions of Halloween-themed avatars and worlds in either the [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat Home|VRChat Home]], Spookality Hub, or a temporary world row. 

The Spookality Jam objective is for creators to hone into the fun of creation and the vibe of the holiday season.

''Check out the [[Special:MyLanguage/Spookality|Spookality]] page for more information.''

=== Pride Month ===
[[File:VRCPrideLogo FullPixel.webp|thumb|Pride Month 2025 banner]]
VRChat celebrates Pride Month every June, acknowledging [[Community:LGBTQ culture in VRChat|LGBTQ culture]] within their community. Starting in 2024, VRChat changed the [[VRChat Home]] with prideful decor for the month of June. Starting in 2025, VRChat is hosting a formal and organized Pride Month series of events, including the following:

* VRChat Home will receive prideful decor, and a charity counter.
* VRChat's charity fundraiser for Trans Lifeline begins on June 11 to June 30.
* Users obtain a unique pride [[Badges|badge]] obtained by gifting [[VRC+]], either through Gift Drops, or by gifting it directly to a user; lasting from June 11 to June 30.
** VRChat will match donations up to $50,000 USD for Trans Lifeline, equivalent to 20% of users' spending on VRC+ gifts.
* VRChat launches the [[Pride Parade Hub World|VRChat Pride Hub World]] on June 11.
** VRChat will livestream the Pride Parade from this world on Twitch, at 2:00 P.M. PST on June 20.
* Users who donate by gifting VRC+ will receive "special surprises" at the end of the month.

=== Flight Week ===
Flight Week is an aviation-themed event organized by VRChat in collaboration with Negentropic, Boeing, and the Australian Government. The event features educational aviation worlds and a curated selection of community-created flight worlds from the international VRChat aviation community.

''Check out the [[Special:MyLanguage/Flight Week|Flight Week]] page for more information.''

