===Avatars for Everyone Jam===
[[File:Avatars for everyone.png|thumb|Avatars for Everyone Jam key art]]
This Jam ran from '''March 2023''' to '''April 2023'''.

The objective of this Jam was to allow the community to bring fresh new avatars to the platform.

Targeting specific aspects of avatar creations, only a fraction of the avatars were selected and even fewer were officially added to the [[Special:MyLanguage/Public Avatars|Public Avatars]].

Some categories allowed participants to win points by following VRChat's guidelines.

Categories:

*Mandatory Rules  
**SDK3
**Compatibility PC / Quest
**Respects TOS
**Mention of third-party apps or stores
*Performance Ranking
*Aesthetics
*Inclusivity
*Avatar Tech
*Balance of features Quest vs PC

