===Space Jam===
[[File:Space Jam .png|thumb|Space Jam key art]]
This Jam ran from '''March 2023''' to '''April 2023'''.

This Jam was built to promote Space Content and push everyone to inspire themselves from the Artemis missions.

This Jam is made in partnership with the [https://nss.org/ National Space Society of Australia (NSSA)]. This allowed this JAM to be backed with prices for the three most inspired and innovative Worlds.

This also allowed the winning worlds to be showcased at the [https://events.humanitix.com/nhs-2024 New Horizons Summit] event.

