===Summer Music Fest Jam===
[[File:Summer Music Fest 2024.png|thumb|right|Summer Music Festival 2024 key art]]
This Jam ran from '''July 8, 2024,''' to '''August 2, 2024'''.

It was planned to promote creativity around music and summer themes. Creators are encouraged to make worlds and avatars regarding this topic.

Promotion of events through those creations is the main objective of this jam within the summer of 2024.

A selection of 10 worlds and 10 avatars, will also be receiving some prices at the end of the JAM.

A VRChat Summer event is also organized in one of the winner worlds featuring DJs from the VRChat dev team on the August 26 2024. 

